- if @notice
  %span.notice{:class => @notice['type']}
    =@notice['msg']
%h2
  New Template Form
%p
  Process (submit to /process) to add / return. Like with the campaign. Upload the template. Store details in Database. Format the name of the file ? encrypt it ? 
%form{:action => "/campaign/#{params[:id]}/template/upload", :method => "post", :enctype => "multipart/form-data"}
  %label{:for => "templatename"} Template Name
  %input{:type => "text", :name => "templatename", :id => "templatename"}
  %br
  %label{:for => "templatefile"} Template File
  %input{:type => "file", :name => "templatefile", :id => "templatefile"}
  %br
  %input{:type => "submit", :value => "Upload"}
